{"tid":1633502,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"聽日戴口罩帶動 「全港學校大致學生情緒的趨勢」","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T15:37:57.000Z","uid":85736,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"46f23d2a2cb35db86b47fd74079dfc53b4b398d6","tid":1633502,"uid":85736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:17:18.000Z","msg":"各位中學雞，聽日一齊戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n各位校友，聽日一齊返母校派口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】<span style=\"color: red;\">教育局要求全港中學周二提交罷課或戴口罩學生人數</span>，中學校長會主席鄧振強相信教育局是希望掌握學生的情緒。<br />\n鄧振強：「<span style=\"color: red;\">他們只是需要提供一個大約的數字</span>，大約的數字可能是以十位數為單位，不需要精準到71個、72個、73個，不會再跟學校核實這些數字。第二我們是不需要提交學生的名字，這個要特別去澄清，不然學生可能會很緊張會有秋後算帳這樣的情況。我不想有太多的陰謀論籠罩着這個社會，我們要用平常心去看，我們只是提交一個大約的數字，<span style=\"color: red;\">讓教育局去掌握全港學校大致學生情緒的趨勢</span>。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365360\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365360&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4o429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=3cafa149\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D365360&h=6602f765\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=365360</a>"},{"pid":"67c0713cfd69b46f315ab0a33dfff590ce797a5e","tid":1633502,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f84f272c64eaf6d6c6e3257bfc23dcc4eeb82b3","tid":1633502,"uid":85736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c0713cfd69b46f315ab0a33dfff590ce797a5e","tid":1633502,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:18:25.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:19:23.000Z","msg":"一齊推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d934153970217bcd317fff296d9a8f251edf2b","tid":163